text: Garrettsburg is an unincorporated community in Buchanan County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Garrettsburg was established in 1872, and remained in operation until 1902. The community has the name of Zach Garrett, a pioneer citizen. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Buchanan County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Garrettsburg, Missouri
